            <title>[CASSANDRA-6803] nodetool getsstables converts key from String incorrectly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6803</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Trivial fix, just need to get the bytebuffer from the CfMetaData&apos;s key validator as opposed to just calling String#getBytes (which is broken for most data types).  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
